I wrote it unclearly, I should have phrased it better, sorry.

What I meant is that I would like to become a committer. I already have a mentor, but if I understood well it is only to deal with the FreeBSD.org account and maybe in the future with a doc commit bit (which I think is the one that is needed for working with quarterly status reports).

So, at the moment,
- I have a mentor for the FreeBSD.org account;
- no one is mentoring me about committing;
- I have no commit bits.
